        "information_danGfx": {
          "type": "information",
          "settings": {
            "title": "INGREDIENTS",
            "text": "<p><strong>Cluster Dextrin</strong>®</p><p>Cluster Dextrin® is known as Highly Branched Cyclic Dextrin (HBCD). Cluster Dextrin® has a high molecular weight and is very fast gastric emptying. This means that it passes through your stomach at a faster rate, compared to other carbohydrate sources, which makes it more readily available for your body to use as energy without stomach discomfort or bloating (due to Cluster Dextrin®'s low osmotic pressure).</p><p>In addition to Cluster Dextrin®'s fast gastric emptying rate, it also provides a sustained release of energy without a sudden spike in blood sugar or insulin response.†</p><p><strong>Electrolytes</strong></p><p>We decided to source the sodium from Pink Himalayan Salt, which is free of additives and naturally contains up to 84 different minerals in trace amounts.</p><p>Our other electrolytes are sourced from Albion®, a trusted source of safe, proven, and effective organic minerals. The proven effectiveness of Albion® minerals, chelated for better absorption, ensures your confidence in our product. They are more easily absorbed into the human body and have been scientifically proven to cause less gastric upset.†</p>"
          }
